elements.name: Verify Error Message for Invalid Mobile Number during Car Insurance Quote

steps.name: I am on the Policybazaar Car Insurance page
I proceed without entering a car number
I select the city
I select the car brand
I select the car model
I select the fuel type
I select the variant
I enter user details with name and invalid mobile number from config
I should see an error message containing "valid" for the mobile number field
I should capture the error message displayed

the user enters mobile number "9876543210" and number of employees "25"
the user clicks on View Plan Instantly
the dialog appears and the user selects "Yes"
